            "period": {
                "glob": "2023 - 2027"
            },
            "description": {
                "nl": "Ik zit momenteel in het derde jaar van mijn opleiding. Tijdens mijn studies heb ik al veel geleerd over vrijwel alle facetten van IT. In het begin lag de focus vooral op programmeren, waardoor ik ervaring heb opgedaan in frontend- en backenddevelopment, objectgeoriënteerd programmeren en zelfs low-level programmeren. Daarna werd de nadruk gelegd op samenwerken via Git en werken met Linux. Momenteel worden we ondergedompeld in DevOps, databases en netwerken. Aan het einde van de opleiding zal de focus liggen op machine learning en cybersecurity.",
                "en": "I am currently in the third year of my studies. During my studies, I have already learned a lot about virtually all aspects of IT. In the beginning, the focus was mainly on programming, which gave me experience in front-end and back-end development, object-oriented programming and even low-level programming. After that, the emphasis shifted to collaborating via Git and working with Linux. Currently, we are immersed in DevOps, databases, and networks. At the end of the programme, the focus will be on machine learning and cybersecurity."
            },
