                "en": "During my high school years, I took on various commitments. For the last four years, I was involved in the student council, serving as chairperson for the last two years. During those last two years, I was also active in the school council. In my final year, together with two friends, I was the main organiser of the school party College TD. In addition, I managed all the finances for the senior activities."
